docs.lead_paragraph: Negotiations which were started some months ago looking to the flotation of a French loan in this country have been practically completed. Announcement of a public offering is looked for soon after July 1. The French will be provided with $100,000,000 on terms a little better than those obtained on the larger Anglo-French loan of five times the amount.
